g.text: Hold Internal Kick-off meeting with Project Manager/CRBRC
Notify potential proposers of upcoming RFP (including DBE)
Meeting #1 with Evaluation Committee to review evaluation process
Send potential proposer list to Procurement Office (including DBE)
Meeting #2 with Evaluation Committee and Project Manager to review and finalize scoring
Check SAM.gov and capture time-stamped screen shot & verify lobbying certification
Initiate contracting process with successful proposer
Send proposals to Evaluation Committee to score according to RFP criteria
Hold Pre-bid Meeting/Site Visit/Q&A Session (not required)
Notify all proposers of evalutation results
Hold oral presentations with top proposers (not required)
Provide answers to submitted questions, as needed
Hold debrief meetings with unsuccessful proposers, as requested
Negotiate scope and fee with successful proposer
